### =============================================
### Veltrix API - Tests d authentification
### =============================================

@base_url = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = REMPLACER_PAR_LE_TOKEN_RECU

### 1. Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

###

### 2. Creer un compte (Register)
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@veltrix-test.com",
  "password": "VeltrixPass1",
  "full_name": "Admin Veltrix",
  "organization_name": "Veltrix Demo Org",
  "phone": "+22890000000"
}

###

### 3. Se connecter (Login)
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@veltrix-test.com",
  "password": "VeltrixPass1"
}

###

### 4. Mon profil (endpoint protege)
GET {{base_url}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Logout
POST {{base_url}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Test erreur - email deja utilise
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@veltrix-test.com",
  "password": "AnotherPass1",
  "full_name": "Doublon",
  "organization_name": "Doublon Org"
}

###

### 7. Test erreur - mauvais mot de passe
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@veltrix-test.com",
  "password": "mauvaismdp"
}

###

### 8. Test erreur - token invalide
GET {{base_url}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer token_invalide_ici

###

### 9. Test erreur - mot de passe trop court
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@test.com",
  "password": "court",
  "full_name": "Test",
  "organization_name": "Test Org"
}
